    "It includes four common spreadsheet tasks: compound interest calculations, date-based logic, inventory restocking, and tiered pricing logic.",
    "For each, we present test cases, a TDD style Python implementation, and an equivalent Excel formula.",
    "These examples are intended only for showing the process by which code can be generated from TDD and as an indicator of the quality of code such a process can yield.",
